graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Operator<br/>Job Queueing Controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Kueue -->|"platform<br/>(required)"| K8s[Kubernetes 1.22+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|"cert provisioning<br/>(optional)"| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Any Version]
    Kueue -.->|"metrics collection<br/>(optional)"| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>PodMonitor]
    Kueue -.->|"autoscaling<br/>(optional)"| ClusterAutoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler<br/>ProvisioningRequests]

    %% Internal RHOAI/ODH Dependencies
    Kueue -->|"webhooks + watch<br/>TFJob, PyTorchJob, MPIJob"| KubeflowTraining[Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>kubeflow.org]
    Kueue -->|"webhooks + watch<br/>RayJob, RayCluster"| RayOperator[Ray Operator<br/>ray.io]
    Kueue -->|"watch<br/>AppWrapper"| CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>workload.codeflare.dev]

    %% External Services (Egress)
    Kueue -->|"watch/manage<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS"| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>CRD Management]
    Kueue -.->|"multi-cluster<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>KubeConfig auth"| RemoteClusters[Remote Kubernetes Clusters<br/>MultiKueue]

    %% Integration Points (Consumers)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|"UI management<br/>(future)"| Kueue
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|"auto-queue jobs<br/>(integration)"| Kueue

    %% Job Framework Integrations (Managed by Kueue)
    Kueue -->|"queue management<br/>webhooks"| BatchJob[Kubernetes Batch Job<br/>batch/v1]
    Kueue -->|"queue management<br/>webhooks"| JobSet[JobSet Controller<br/>jobset.x-k8s.io]

    %% Observability
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|"scrapes metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP"| Kueue

